a's cup of coffee", "timestamp": 1774945793}, {"author": "penamartinezeduardo", "author_id": "3403826762", "id": "17879608560514972", "text": "", "timestamp": 1774937325}, {"author": "shudel", "author_id": "302614109", "id": "18091575602126516", "text": "👏👏👏", "timestamp": 1774727092}, {"author": "catherine.dyson.10", "author_id": "9872975649", "id": "18105212899904101", "text": "Inspiring!", "timestamp": 1774408542}, {"author": "gingerstormer", "author_id": "704406231", "id": "17902188639402260", "text": "I used this very song to teach musical theatre to young kids….i had no experience but figured I could make this song work, and it DID!!! Parents dug it and the kids LOVED IT!", "timestamp": 1774308487}, {"author": "one_angry_biker", "author_id": "27708471898", "id": "17964192491898622", "text": "", "timestamp": 1774159090}, {"author": "srampelberg", "author_id": "60523316260", "id": "18096818353823282", "text": "❤️", "timestamp": 1773943825}, {"author": "irishpetemoss", "author_id": "48785638099", "id": "18065612093654431", "text": "Insert  Full Metal Jacket😎", "timestamp": 1773861815}, {"author": "justleslienicole", "author_id": "3159994709", "id": "18117009043650211", "text": "This was one of my Dad’s favorite songs.", "timestamp": 1773812619}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/586714811_18057312719645280_8167104934333489797_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi41NDB4OTYwLnNkci5mODI3ODcuZGVmYXVsdF9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHoUvPZD2dvLV3beaaq5Br-0GUI1SPZQALM7IYq-yHwIZdtVvUeKks2icRI07m3z1g&_nc_ohc=xdxixGu68FwQ7kNvwEksMPF&_nc_gid=n0RMPP8mpPnpraexG8uF_Q&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af3kBCQzrR0GTpWjd6SdOsJrLjgwRDc39nsLKYdo7mTWnA&oe=69D4D583&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1137, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1137"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/586714811_18057312719645280_8167104934333